==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Danewort
<hw>Dane"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
fetid European species of elder (<spn>Sambucus Ebulus</spn>); dwarf
elder; wallwort; elderwort; -- called also <altname>Daneweed</altname>,
<altname>Dane's weed</altname>, and <altname>Dane's-blood</altname>.
<note>[Said to grow on spots where battles were fought against the
Danes.]</note></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dang</ent>⟦br⟧
